lead_paragraph: Svetlana Kuznetsova erased 12 of the 14 break points she faced and beat Timea Bacsinszky, 7-5, 6-3, on Thursday in the semifinals of the Miami Open in Key Biscayne, Fla.

headline.print_headline: No. 19 Svetlana Kuznetsova Reaches Miami Open Final
headline.main: No. 19 Svetlana Kuznetsova Reaches Miami Open Final
